serialdaemon.c

Allows you to connect a socket with a serial port, for languages (such 
as Java) which do not play nicely with serial ports but which talk to 
sockets just fine.

serialdaemon_win32.zip

Recompilation of serialdaemon.c for Windows, including executable.

SocketDaemon.java

Essentially a simple router which listens in on a local socket and 
forwards all the traffic to a remote machine.  We used this on panda to 
enable an outside computer to talk to the socket on a local flockbot.
